    <item>
      <title>HODL</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/glossary/hodl/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 May 2025 17:55:02 +0530</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/glossary/hodl/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;HODL is a slang term in the cryptocurrency community that originated from a misspelled word &amp;ldquo;hold.&amp;rdquo; It refers to the strategy of holding onto cryptocurrencies for a long period of time instead of selling them, even during high market volatility. It embodies a belief in the long-term value and potential of a cryptocurrency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Origin&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;origin&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#origin&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The term comes from a 2013 post on the BitcoinTalk forum titled “I AM HODLING” by a user who drunkenly misspelled “holding.” The typo went viral and became an acronym for “Hold On for Dear Life.”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HODL has evolved to symbolize steadfast belief in the long-term success of crypto assets. It’s often used to resist panic-selling during market dips or crashes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Usage&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#usage&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Basic usage:&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;basic-usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#basic-usage&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Bitcoin is down 30% this week, but I’m going to HODL. I believe in its long-term value.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;In a tweet or meme:&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;in-a-tweet-or-meme&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#in-a-tweet-or-meme&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Markets are red, portfolios are bleeding, but real degens HODL!&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Investor strategy:&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;investor-strategy&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#investor-strategy&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;She bought Ethereum in 2016 and decided to HODL. Now, it&#39;s one of her best-performing investments.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;In contrast to trading:&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;in-contrast-to-trading&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#in-contrast-to-trading&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;While traders try to time the market, I just HODL and accumulate more when prices dip.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;As a rallying cry:&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;as-a-rallying-cry&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#as-a-rallying-cry&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The crypto crash is temporary. Remember: HODL strong!&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
